node.text:
Have you heard the news? I’ve joined Merryfield as Co-Founder and Chief Creative Officer. Yay! What’s Merryfield? So glad you asked! It’s a new app, a rewards program exclusively for better-for-you, purpose-led brands like Stonyfield, The Honest Company, Califia Farms, and other amazing brands. 

Making more informed, positive decisions for me and my family makes me feel good, and I know a lot of people feel the same way. 

What’s so special about Merryfield? It’s the only rewards app with rigorous quality standards that all brands and products must meet to be on the app. 

And let’s face it, money matters! We want to make it easier and more rewarding for all of us to support clean-label, socially and environmentally responsible brands. The choices we all make every day on everyday products can make a world of difference! Let’s all vote with our dollars! 

Ready to join me at Merryfield? Check the link in my bio to download the free iOs app (Android coming soon!) to get started! One more thing: Tell us in the comments which of your favorite better-for-you brands we should add next to the app! xx, Zooey
